              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation/clbeacon/1621418-major"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation/clbeacon/1621558-minor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties. These values are coded into the beacon itself. For a more thorough description of the meaning of those values, see "
